Chinese Patent Data

Column

Description

All patents registered in China National Intellectual Property Administration (CNIPA)

  • Source: https://www.cnipa.gov.cn, https://patent.google.com
  • Period：1985-2021
  • Observations：Around 19,000,000 patents.
